column5: Couldn't make it by today,but is that still on?. I have one or two I wouldn't give to my worst enemy. If it is how much per hundred dollars? Thanks.
You have til tomorrow the 14th. The rod trade ins are March 16-20.
Depends on how much you buy a new reel for  Anything from $5-$100.

Thanks Bill,but when I was there Yesterday they had a bait caster with a computer chip for $799.00. Remembers everything. Low profile .That is almost a little to much in my opinion. But given the windfalls in tournaments, I guess it could make a difference?. Wow.
Calais DC   Nice reel!  I bought my reel (Normal Calais) for a steal compared to what they sell it there for new (I think $599 or something crazy like that)
Traded in a crappy reel that sells for $19.99 and got $40 off a chronarch..
Oh and the offer ends tomorrow
not worth it!!!  ....dont ask me how i know.....
